General.Name: Labrador Uranium Inc
General.Description: Latitude Uranium Inc. engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of mineral properties in Labrador, Canada. It primarily explores for uranium. The company focuses on the Angilak Property located in Nunavut Territory, Canada. The company was formerly known as Labrador Uranium Inc. and changed its name to Latitude Uranium Inc. in June 2023. The company was incorporated in 2021 and is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
